net.minecraftforge.common.util

クラス Constants.WorldEvents

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.minecraftforge.common.util.Constants.WorldEvents
  • 含まれているクラス:
    Constants

    public static class Constants.WorldEvents
extends java.lang.Object
    The world event IDS, used when calling IWorld.playEvent(int, BlockPos, int).
    Can be found from WorldRenderer.playEvent(net.minecraft.entity.player.PlayerEntity, int, net.minecraft.util.math.BlockPos, int)
    Some of the events use the data parameter. If this is the case, an explanation of what data does is also provided
